00:13:45.366 --> 00:13:47.436 A:middle
So it all starts at the screen
level and the screen's going

00:13:47.436 --> 00:13:48.476 A:middle
to have a trait collection.

00:13:48.806 --> 00:13:52.166 A:middle
What's important to note about
this is that the every device

00:13:52.166 --> 00:13:53.876 A:middle
and orientation and
adaptation is going

00:13:53.876 --> 00:13:56.366 A:middle
to have a fully specified
trait collection.

00:13:56.686 --> 00:13:57.496 A:middle
And what I mean by that is

00:13:57.496 --> 00:14:00.046 A:middle
that all the different traits
are going to have values.

00:13:57.496 --> 00:14:00.046 A:middle
